preference.name: AIE_HM_master_ds_tools
preference.preference_description: Preference to indicate the Teamcenter tools that correspond to each AIE_<APP>_master_ds_types listed in the preference AIE_HM_master_ds_types. There must be one and only one for each master dataset type and have to be in the same order. APP must match one of the values in AIE_master_family_list.
